The '''Crawler''', also known as the '''CRAWL''' , is an enemy in ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It can be found exclusively within the [[Marsh Cave]], where it can be encountered alongside the [[Bloodbones (Final Fantasy)|Bloodbones]] or the [[Skeleton (Final Fantasy)|Skeleton]]. It is one of multiple enemies in the dungeon capable of inflicting [[Paralysis (Final Fantasy status)|Paralysis]] with its attacks, with its high hit count of 8 giving it the greatest chance of all of them to successfully inflict the status. This makes it one of the more dangerous enemies in the dungeon despite its low damage output, and therefore strongly recommended to take out quickly in encounters where it is present.

