== Battle ==
[[File:Amano Gigas Worm.gif|thumb|Concept artwork by [[Yoshitaka Amano]].]]
The Crawler has a low Attack stat, but its attacks have a high chance of causing [[Paralysis]], and it gets a staggering number of hits—it can easily hit eight times in one attack action. This makes the Crawler a particular menace among enemies found in the Marsh Cave, as their paralyzing attacks can easily put party members out of commission, and they are resilient enough relative to the party's likely capabilities that taking them out swiftly to minimize party member paralysis may prove a challenging endeavor.

